@startuml C4_Manage_Qualifications_Logical_View
title C4 – PLMS – Logical View (Manage Qualifications)
left to right direction

skinparam node {
  BackgroundColor White
  BorderColor Black
  FontColor Black
  FontStyle bold
}
skinparam cloud {
  BackgroundColor LightGray
  BorderColor Black
  FontColor Black
}
skinparam database {
  BackgroundColor Wheat
  BorderColor Black
  FontColor Black
}
skinparam artifact {
  BackgroundColor HoneyDew
  BorderColor Black
  FontColor Black
}

actor "Port Authority Officer" as Officer

node "User Device\n(Laptop / Browser)" as Client {
  artifact "Frontend Web App\n(React / Angular)" as Frontend
}

node "Application Server\n(Docker Container / IIS)" as AppServer {
  artifact "Qualifications Management API\n(ASP.NET Core Web API)" as API
}

node "Database Server\n(SQL Server / InMemory)" as DBServer {
  database "PLMS Database" as Database
}

cloud "External IAM Provider\n(OAuth 2.0 / OpenId Connect)" as IAM

Officer --> Frontend : Accesses via Browser (HTTPS)
Frontend --> API : REST / JSON
API --> IAM : Validates Token
API --> Database : CRUD via EF Core (SQL)

@enduml
